      • CheckResult

        public CheckResult(Command command,
                   java.lang.String json)
            throws CheckResult.MalformedJsonException
        Parses the given JSON string, setting check, outcome, and diagnostic member variables when found accordingly.

        This method assumes the json passed represents only one result, and any duplicates will overwrite values.

        Parameters:
        command - the command run
        json - the json to parse
        Throws:
        CheckResult.MalformedJsonException - if the json given is not valid for a CheckResult
